## Frequently Asked Questions

**Can you achieve Korean hair colors on dark hair without bleaching?**
Many Korean colors — like milk tea brown, dark chocolate and copper — can be achieved on dark hair with minimal or no bleaching. For blonde or grey shades, some bleaching is usually required. We'll advise you honestly during consultation.

**How long does color last?**
Most semi-permanent colors last 4–8 weeks. Permanent color lasts until it grows out. We'll recommend the best option for your lifestyle and maintenance preferences.

**Do I need to do anything before my color appointment?**
Come with clean, dry hair if possible. Avoid heavy styling products. And most importantly — bring reference photos!

